        "timestamp": "2018-11-19 13:15:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 11:\n\nHi,\n\nI have a question regarding the design.\nIn a scenario in which I copy an instance and then not immediately pasting it instead I continue working in the composition tab and after a while I want to paste it, or even the opposite. I accidentally paste it, I don't have any visual sign of which instance has been copied.\nIn more complex situation this could be a problem for the user.\nIs this something that is resolvable? \nAdding some kind of visual representation of the copied instance?",
        "patchset_number": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "74f05f4fe59efd9c87ed7fd70523a5d3b4c73a50",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3643,
