        "timestamp": "2018-12-23 17:04:40.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 12:\n\nHi, please apply the following:\n\nPosition of the pasted item-\nAfter pasting, the pasted item should be placed in a constant place.\nWe may want to place the pasted item right next to the copied item so even when there are many items on the canvas, the user would know where to find it.\n\nSelected item after pasting-\nCurrent behavior: After pasting, the original item is selected\nDesired behavior: after pasting, the pasted item is selected.\n\nThanks",
        "patchset_number": 12
      },
